      <h1>About Kushiro</h1>
      <p>Welcome to <strong>Kushiro</strong>!</p>
      <p>
        Kushiro is a simple yet delightful tool designed to bring a spark of spontaneity to your anime-watching journey. By connecting to your 
        <strong>MyAnimeList (MAL)</strong> account, Kushiro fetches and displays a random anime from your "Plan to Watch" list.
      </p>
      <h2>Why Kushiro?</h2>
      <p>
        We know the struggle of deciding what to watch next from an ever-growing list of anime. Kushiro takes that burden off your shoulders and surprises you with a random pick. It's like rolling the dice, but for anime lovers!
      </p>
      <h2>Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Random Anime Selection:</strong> Get a randomly chosen anime from your "Plan to Watch" list.</li>
        <li><strong>Detailed Information:</strong> View the anime's name, rating, genres, status, and synopsis.</li>
        <li><strong>Clean and Responsive Design:</strong> Enjoy a seamless experience across all devices.</li>
      </ul>
      <h2>Who Can Use Kushiro?</h2>
      <p>
        Whether you're a seasoned anime enthusiast or a newcomer exploring the world of anime, Kushiro is here to guide your next watch.
      </p>
      <p class="cta">So why wait? Connect your MyAnimeList profile and let Kushiro decide your next anime adventure!</p>
    </section>
  </main>
